BY BODE GBADEBO, Abuja  | President of the Senate, Senator Ahmad Lawan, has felicitated with the Governor of Yobe State, Mai Mala Buni, as he marks his 53rd birthday today. Lawan joined the family, friends and political associates of the Governor as well as the entire people of Yobe State in celebrating the occasion. According to a statement signed by the media adviser to the Senate President, Ola Awoniyi, on Wednesday, Lawan was quoted as saying that the occasion was worthy of celebration because Governor Buni has devoted his life to the service of his people and excelled in the calling. “I rejoice with His Excellency, members of his family, friends, political associates and our good people of Yobe State on this auspicious occasion. “It is particularly worthy of note the giant strides the administration of Governor Buni has made in just 17 months in Yobe, which are visible in improved security, infrastructure and general economic development of the state.